Class Symbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.binghamton.jhelp.Symbol
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MethodSymbol, Type, VariableSymbol

    public abstract class Symbol
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing the abstract notion of a Java symbol Java symbols include classes, enums, interfaces, methods, and variables
